/**************************************************************************************
 *                               Hangman 3.0
 * 
 * Welcome to Hangman! This suite is designed to provide a suite of tools to play 
 * around with the game of Hangman.
 * 
 * Features:
 *    -Provides objects and methods with which to play the game of Hangman, using a 
 *     random game. Game can now be played from the command line,
 *     with full functionality.
 *
 * 
 * Planned Updates: 
 *    -Human playing:
 *       -Start game from a string
 *       -Control length of random game
 *       -Select from a list of phrases for a random game, rather than random words
 *    -AI playing:
 *       -Various AI solvers:
 *          -Random
 *          -Brute force
 *          -Letter frequency
 *       -Tools to compare solvers:
 *          -Running time comparison
 *          -Guess comparison
 *    -Overarching tools package
 *       -Used outside of this application
 *          -Allows user to pull any of the features
 